io.tesler.core.diag.jdbc

Class CompoundJdbcEventListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.p6spy.engine.event.JdbcEventListener
      • io.tesler.core.diag.jdbc.CompoundJdbcEventListener

  • public class CompoundJdbcEventListener
extends com.p6spy.engine.event.JdbcEventListener
    Implements only some of the methods, since there are methods, which are executed quite often and therefore provide performance impact, e.g. onAfterResultSetGet
